title: los vikingos
description:
Sweeping adventure saga of the Vikings\&#039; invasion of England centers on a Viking warrior prince (Kirk Douglas) and a former slave (Tony Curtis), bitter enemies and unwitting half brothers who clash over control of the British kingdom of Northumbria and the love of a beautiful English princess (Janet Leigh). Ernest Borgnine also stars with Orson Welles serving as narrator. Filmed on location in Norway; directed by Richard Fleischer. 124 min.
